    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121510/extras/f766f1ab1266e5055a8217d585cd2b19.poster.avif?t=1771157479\" width=616 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121510/extras/f766f1ab1266e5055a8217d585cd2b19.webm?t=1771157479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121510/extras/f766f1ab1266e5055a8217d585cd2b19.mp4?t=1771157479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tenebris Somnia</strong> is a survival horror adventure game in the same vein as classics like <i>Silent Hill</i> or <i>Resident Evil</i> - but adapted to a retro 2D aesthetic from the 8 or 16-bit era.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will struggle to survive while solving puzzles and fighting <strong>horrible</strong> creatures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yet the secrets of the game lie within its <strong>cinematics...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you reach certain key points you will see sequences from a <strong>completely</strong> different point of view, made in live action with real actors and practical effects - created by a professional and award winning film crew from Argentina.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121510/extras/5fd5d86aebd202f0e6a984b06de439c0.poster.avif?t=1771157479\" width=616 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121510/extras/5fd5d86aebd202f0e6a984b06de439c0.webm?t=1771157479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121510/extras/5fd5d86aebd202f0e6a984b06de439c0.mp4?t=1771157479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
